{"tid":1217823,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)白事可樂 北韓給你五星級的家","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T18:37:29.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"610a7e8b94cd0f142aca288e6ef5031a0dc62ef8","tid":1217823,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=aef56063\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=38ca2dfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=55f13667\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9f/Newworldwarzpostersmall.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9f%2FNewworldwarzpostersmall.jpg&h=c21a4019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cb/The_Interview_2014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcb%2FThe_Interview_2014.jpg&h=a3a78aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.前聯合國調查員傑瑞&middot;藍恩與自己的妻子凱倫和兩個女兒瑞秋與康妮，愉快的在擁擠的費城市區公路上行車，但一分鐘內就有多架直升機從空中飛過，而新聞上一直在談論關於台灣爆發的狂犬病毒。突然間，公路前方發生了爆炸，而公路上執勤的警察當場被失控的垃圾車撞死，傑瑞跟隨垃圾車的行進路線離開公路，之後與一輛失控的救護車發生相撞。傑瑞與凱倫回過神來後，帶著女兒們丟下汽車逃跑，而廣場上也轉眼間出現了幾百名瘋狂咬人的殭屍，而傑瑞與家人逃離時親眼看到一名被殭屍咬到的人，在十二秒之內也淪為了一個殭屍，後來與家人開著一輛房車逃離了城市。不到兩小時，費城淪陷，美軍阻止殭屍的軍事行動全部以失敗告終...<br />\n<br />\n一位美國脫口秀主持人David Skylark（詹姆斯&middot;法蘭科飾）和他的製作人亞倫&middot;拉波波特（塞斯&middot;羅根飾）得知現任北韓最高領導人金正恩是他們的節目《今夜胡鬧秀》（Skylark Tonight）的粉絲，於是他們決定採訪金正恩。在他們準備踏上北韓土地的時候，美國中央情報局卻徵集他們倆去暗殺金正恩........<br />\n<br />\n10 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D屍集體衝埋黎真係有槍都檔唔住 要小令森D<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=4b242d6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=fd1d57d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b262d55dbd0140411bcfeeda28f9797622c0630d","tid":1217823,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9665894cf748